title: Limits
description: Marcia, Phil and Ben take a trip to the Bronx to meet Reed Richard’s young protegé, Charlie Martinez, to try and solve the mystery of how the leader of The Fantastic Four pulled off such a massive hoax.Starring AnnaSophia Robb as Marcia Hardesty; Seth Barrish as Phil Sheldon; Method Man as Ben Urich; Gabriela Ortega as Charlie Martinez; Daniel Molina as The Silver Surfer.
author: originals@stitcher.com (MARVELS)
